      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="spark-orb">
          <img src="/guilty-spark-h3.png" alt="343 Guilty Spark" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section id="features" class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          <span class="section-title-line"></span>
          CORE SYSTEMS
          <span class="section-title-line"></span>
        </h2>

        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üìä</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Match Statistics</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              I shall retrieve comprehensive combat records from the Waypoint archives. All performance
              data‚Äîeliminations, objectives, efficiency metrics‚Äîrendered in detailed analytical displays.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <img src="/neatqueue-logo.png" alt="NeatQueue" class="feature-icon-img" />
            <h3 class="feature-title">NeatQueue Integration</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Integration established. I have interfaced with the queue management construct to provide automated
              statistical analysis upon match completion. Most efficient.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üó∫Ô∏è</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">HCS Map Generator</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Generating map and mode combinations based on HCS specifications or other parameters matching
              requirements. Randomized selection parameters ensure competitive balance across all engagement zones.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon-live">‚óè</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Live Match Tracking</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Real-time telemetry monitoring is active. I shall provide continuous updates on ongoing combat scenarios
              as data streams become available, including live scores displayed in channel names.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üîó</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Account Linking</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Reclaimers may synchronize their Discord identities with Xbox service records using the <code
                >/connect</code
              > command. I shall query the necessary databases automatically once permissions are granted.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Configuration</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Initialization procedures are straightforward. I shall guide you through all necessary parameters using
              the <code>/setup</code> command‚Äîdisplay preferences, channel assignments, webhook authentication.
            </p>
