      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          <span class="section-title-line"></span>
          INITIALIZATION PROTOCOL
          <span class="section-title-line"></span>
        </h2>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3 class="step-title">Add to Discord</h3>
              <p class="step-description">
                Authorize my presence in your Discord server. I require minimal permissions: message posting, embed
                generation, and webhook management for automated reporting.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3 class="step-title">Link Your Account</h3>
              <p class="step-description">
                Use the <code>/connect</code> command to synchronize your Discord identity with your Xbox service record.
                This enables me to retrieve your combat data from the Waypoint archives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3 class="step-title">Query Statistics</h3>
              <p class="step-description">
                Access comprehensive match analytics with simple commands. I shall compile performance metrics, combat
                ratings, and engagement summaries from your service history.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2 class="cta-title">Initiate Integration Protocol</h2>
          <p class="cta-description">
            I am currently assisting 18 Discord installations with their combat analytics. Over 1000 match series have
            been analyzed and archived. Your installation may proceed immediately.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a
              href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1290269474536034357&permissions=311385476096&integration_type=0&scope=bot+applications.commands"
              target="_blank"
              class="btn btn-primary btn-large"
            >
              <img src="/discord-logo.png" alt="" class="btn-icon-img" />
              Authorize Installation
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="cta-note">
            Require assistance? Access our <a href="https://discord.gg/WS7zG8GDKY" target="_blank"
              >support installation</a
            > for guidance protocols.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">
      <span class="section-title-line"></span>
      RECLAIMER INQUIRIES
      <span class="section-title-line"></span>
    </h2>

    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">How do I synchronize my Xbox service record?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          Use the <code>/connect</code> command. I shall query the Xbox database for your service tag, verify the correct
          identity match, and establish a persistent link to your Discord designation. Once synchronized, I will automatically
          retrieve your performance data during monitored engagements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">What if privacy restrictions are enabled?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          I operate within the parameters established by Waypoint authorization protocols. Should your record contain
          privacy restrictions, I shall inform you accordingly. For optimal functionality, ensure your Halo Infinite
          profile visibility settings permit external queries through Xbox privacy controls.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Which playlists are supported?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          I maintain compatibility with HCS maps and modes, as well as most ranked playlists. The <code>/maps</code>
          command specifically generates HCS tournament combinations, or can be customized to your specifications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Are there operational costs?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          Negative. My services require no currency exchange, subscription fees, or premium tier access. Operational
          expenses are covered to ensure all functions remain accessible without limitation to the community. However,
          if you wish to support continued development and expanded capabilities, contributions may be made through
          <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/davidhouweling" target="_blank" class="faq-link">GitHub Sponsors</a>.
          Your backing enables sustained operational efficiency and new feature development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

